OL,3,CNorthern Ireland's unpaid carers being
OL,4,Cleft behind by new law, campaigners
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FWorkers are entitled to such leave to
OL,8,Fgive or arrange care for a dependant `
OL,9,Fnot necessarily a family member ` who
OL,10,Fhas a physical or mental illness or
OL,11,Finjury meaning they will need care for
OL,12,Fmore than three months, who has a
OL,13,Fdisability, or who needs care due to
OL,14,Fold age.
OL,16,FThe new legislation will not cover
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland where employment
OL,18,Frules are devolved to Stormont.
