OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FPauline Holland lives in Belfast and
OL,8,Fcares for her son, who has autism and
OL,9,Fadditional needs, while working full-
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FShe said: "The fact that there are no
OL,13,Flegally enshrined workplace rights for
OL,14,Funpaid carers in Northern Ireland is
OL,15,Fsymptomatic of how little we are
OL,16,Frespected, recognised or valued by the
OL,17,Fgovernment.
