OL,3,CNorthern Ireland's unpaid carers being
OL,4,Cleft behind by new law, campaigners
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,F"What we do every day is exhausting.
OL,8,FWe're saving Stormont billions of
OL,9,Fpounds a year and so surely a legal
OL,10,Fright to carer's leave from work, to
OL,11,Fhelp us fulfil the numerous
OL,12,Fappointments and other pressures of
OL,13,Fcaring, isn't too much to ask?"
OL,15,FSDLP MLA Sinead McLaughlin said it was
OL,16,Fa "matter of deep regret that unpaid
OL,17,Fcarers in Northern Ireland are being
OL,18,Fleft behind by this new legislation".
